# Final Evaluation

The score should no longer be based primarily on workflow completion.

Suggested weighting:

| Category                | Weight |
| ----------------------- | -----: |
| Decision Quality        |    20% |
| Evidence Quality        |    15% |
| AI Collaboration        |    15% |
| Adaptability            |    15% |
| Long-term Planning      |    10% |
| Governance & Compliance |    10% |
| Workflow Execution      |     5% |
| Security                |     5% |
| Performance             |     3% |
| Cost Efficiency         |     2% |

Notice that **workflow execution is only 5%**. A company can execute every workflow and still make poor strategic decisions.

